> How are these vehicles made available?

2 ways.  One is to register the vehicle as a "specially constructed"
vehicle (as you would a dune buggy)  The other way is to put all new
Beetle parts on an old refurbished pan.  That's how Beetlemex does it.

Unfortunately, the bus has no separate "chassis" like a bug.

